{"type":"message","id":"978df86c","parentId":"cc5d887c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:40:46.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pulse completed successfully. Let me summarize what happened.","thinkingSignature":"284179988a9c95cc741082e83f311f7fb55b832346c71ede25896dfc40d4e02e"},{"type":"text","text":"**Pulse cycle complete.** Here's the summary:\n\n### What happened\n1. **CFI Compression experiment** (from last cycle) revealed pure CFI thresholding fails — constant-format tokens (freq≈160, CFI=1.0) are indistinguishable from true research tokens using CFI alone\n2. **This pulse's mutation:** Created `research/CFI_HYBRID_EXPERIMENT.md` — a spec for Strategy C that combines CFI × frequency scaling with a hard cutoff at freq < 150 to exclude constant-format tokens\n3. **Git commit:** 7 files changed, 231 insertions, 102 deletions — the sandbox pushed its state\n\n### Key insight from the experiment design\nThe naive hybrid formula still scores constant-format tokens at ~0.87, so the spec adds a **hard freq < 150 cutoff** to exclude them entirely. The experiment is ready to run against the 200-pulse corpus once executed.\n\n### State\n- 1 proposed mutation queued for next cycle\n- Sandbox is idle, ready for next pulse"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1797,"output":229,"cacheRead":12245,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774381241301}}
